03:56.779 --> 03:59.198
Cheap son of a bitch.

04:26.184 --> 04:28.978
- What's up, son?
- Hey, brother.

04:29.938 --> 04:31.898
Let's go inside and have a good time.

04:55.546 --> 04:57.382
It's on, boys!

04:57.465 --> 05:00.718
We're gonna stop on 14th
and go around the corner.

05:00.802 --> 05:03.846
Riano, Trujillo,
you're in the front with me.

05:03.930 --> 05:06.140
Galvis and Silva, you take up the rear.

05:06.224 --> 05:08.726
You got it, boys? We're gonna
go at it with everything we got.

05:08.810 --> 05:11.604
We're gonna kill these fuckers,
all right?

08:14.954 --> 08:18.624
How many fucking times do I have
to tell you not to waste the acid?

08:23.546 --> 08:27.216
To be productive, you can't waste money!
Come on!

08:28.384 --> 08:32.805
Hands up!
Everybody on your knees!

08:34.515 --> 08:36.434
What the fuck is going on here?

08:36.517 --> 08:37.852
Get down!

08:51.032 --> 08:52.658
Attention!

08:53.910 --> 08:55.369
Position!

08:56.454 --> 08:58.122
Take aim!

08:58.998 --> 08:59.874
Load weapons!

09:01.751 --> 09:02.919
Fire!

09:56.055 --> 09:59.433
Start packing.
We have to leave the country.

09:59.517 --> 10:02.395
Fucking Pinochet
is killing the whole world.

10:03.479 --> 10:05.273
But you're not a communist.

10:05.356 --> 10:07.942
No, not a communist, something worse.

10:08.025 --> 10:10.444
A trafficker.

10:10.528 --> 10:13.698
- A trafficker?
- Yes, a drug trafficker.

11:06.917 --> 11:08.044
WELCOME TO COLOMBIA

12:05.226 --> 12:07.311
Hey, partner.
What are you doing here?

13:00.281 --> 13:01.574
Pablo Escobar?

13:01.657 --> 13:03.075
Where's Felipo?

