13:25.306 --> 13:27.308
You're Colonel Jose Luis Herrera.

13:30.269 --> 13:32.021
And that's Nacho Ibarra.

13:35.065 --> 13:39.069
There's Garcia, Lopez...

13:39.153 --> 13:41.197
- Is that Pinilla?
- Yes, Pinilla.

13:41.280 --> 13:42.239
That's Pinilla.

13:42.323 --> 13:43.991
Pinilla...

13:44.074 --> 13:45.910
and with Phillipe is Esparanza.

13:45.993 --> 13:48.078
I don't give a rat's ass.
Open the fucking trucks.

13:48.162 --> 13:49.705
